---
title: Saucy Beyond Meat® Ragù with Olive Tapenade
description: This twist on the classic spaghetti Bolognese is a winner! Penne replaces spaghetti, while the ragù is packed with Beyond Meat® and tons of flavour! Topped with a fresh olive tapenade, this dish will have everyone in your home going back for seconds!
